headline: Trump Wants RFK Jr. To 'Go Wild' On Health Care. What This Means For Biotech Stocks.
summary: Robert F. Kennedy Jr. is the new Health Secretary. From fluoride, vaccines and beef tallow, here's how he might "go wild" on biotech stocks.
